This mini project is a web application that enables users to create and manage movie reviews using a tech stack of ReactJS, Spring Boot, and MongoDB. The application features key functionalities, including a user-friendly interface for submitting reviews, viewing a complete list of movies, and retrieving detailed information about films using their IMDb IDs. Users can securely register and log in, allowing them to contribute ratings and comments on their favorite movies. The application employs a RESTful API for seamless communication between the frontend and backend, facilitating efficient data management. With a focus on enhancing user experience and showcasing modern web development practices, this project serves as a valuable platform for movie enthusiasts to engage with and share their insights on films.
